"code_caption","text":"AlipayJSBridgeReady 调用方法代码示例：","id":"60aa9d76-cfe9-4e22-a192-11ac33c3177d","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[612,792],"block_position":"3-1"},{"bbox":[46,113,562,381],"index":2,"angle":0,"type":"code","text":"```html\n1 <script>\n2 //备注:\n3 //无需另外引入js，参照下文开发联调方式生成二维码，线上郑好办扫一扫即可\n4 function ready(callback) {\n5 if (window.AlipayJSBridge) {\n6 callback && callback();\n7 } else {\n8 document.addEventListener('AlipayJSBridgeReady', callback, false);\n9 }\n10 }\n11 ready(function(){\n12 alert('bridge ready');\n13 });\n14 </script>\n```","id":"e8d4e673-3c56-400e-b599-bb1fba3a6f1d","color":{"line":"rgba(200, 140, 58, 1)","fill":"rgba(200, 140, 58, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"page_size":[612,792],"block_position":"3-2"},{"bbox":[45,396,220,415],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"# 2、获取用户授权码JSAPI","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":3,"id":"b272f348-b95f-4559-8e10-d7f2daba0cae","page_size":[612,792],"block_position":"3-3"},{"bbox":[44,422,556,456],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":4,"text":"该JSAPI会判断用户是否登录，如果用户未登录，客户端会处理登录逻辑，前端无感知，无需前端项目主动调用登录","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"6f992b44-3575-48f7-af6d-8f04da531651","page_size":[612,792],"block_position":"3-4"},{"bbox":[556,771,563,780],"type":"page_number","angle":0,"index":1000004,"text":"4","color":{"line":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)","fill":"rgba(164, 164, 164, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"is_discarded":true,"id":"d6f4ba67-6dba-4b11-9f96-4344739a5b89","page_size":[612,792],"block_position":"3-5"}],[{"bbox":[46,34,564,321],"index":0,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/788ab6e37ff4c544d5266dd06a2c861d58ffd6571e030c037aae5adcff706c38.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.8464052287581699,"page_idx":4,"id":"d4f41e83-e41c-4ccb-818d-769dd73ab6a4","page_size":[612,792],"block_position":"4-0"},{"bbox":[